{"tid":1162673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍艦再駛入南海黃岩島12海里處","createTime":"2019-05-20T04:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T04:22:34.000Z","uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc5ed914e703aab33cdbbbb9793df914ec38952","tid":1162673,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:08:51.000Z","msg":"路透報道，美國軍方再次放出風聲，稱導彈驅逐艦普雷貝爾號(USS Preble)在南海執行自由航行任務，且進入了黃岩島12海里處航行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國官方尚未對此作出回應</strong></span>，此前美艦在南海的多次挑釁行動，均被解放軍查證識別、警告驅離。<br />\n<br />\n路透引述第七艦隊發言人Clay Doss稱，普雷布爾號驅逐艦進入黃岩島12海里範圍內航行，以挑戰過度的領海主張，並根據國際法保護水路通道。<br />\n<br />\n5月6日，美國海軍普雷貝爾號、鍾雲號(USS Chung-Hoon)驅逐艦曾進入中國南海島礁鄰近海域。解放軍南部戰區新聞發言人李華敏當時表示，解放軍南部戰區組織有關海空兵力，依法依規對美艦進行了識別查證，予以警告驅離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2141267/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2141267%2F&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=aa7dca5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2141267/</a>"},{"pid":"9b44a70c796a6e75fdceeb1561960e0c03277650","tid":1162673,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"口交部應該研發更強硬回應"},{"pid":"3159732dd35a06ee94dad825c1aa2a162e4ee6fc","tid":1162673,"uid":249604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ae1790240fe0ae369ae75d31307d7442183c5cc","tid":1162673,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>此前美艦在南海的多次挑釁行動，均被解放軍查證識別、警告驅離。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實情：跟尾狗係後面狗吠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613e72fae35bdc3470cd268490519e06806b4307","tid":1162673,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"軍事 經濟 政治夾擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}